org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.states

Class MoveWithPID

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.states.AbState
      • org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.states.MoveWithPID
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    IterativeMoveState, MoveToAvoid

    public class MoveWithPID
extends AbState
    MoveWithPID uses PIDs to move directly to the specified target. It is also the super class to IterativeMoveState and MoveToAvoid.
    Author:
    Will (wrtc9)
